[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    132[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mProblem:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m The Bedrock paragraph correctly names the productivity-tool framing ("Always with human review; the LLM is producing decision support, not decisions") and includes the right HTML-comment TODO acknowledging that the HIPAA-eligible Bedrock model list shifts. The Step 6 pseudocode uses [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mmodel_id = "anthropic.claude-XX"[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m which is appropriately abstract about the specific Anthropic version. The temperature=0.0 setting is the right discipline for a clinical-decision-support narrative.[K
