[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    445[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106mEach path has different security posture (mutual TLS vs OAuth vs SFTP-with-SSH-keys vs S/MIME) and different network requirements (some paths require Direct Connect to hospital network for HIE-side bridging, some use AWS Transfer Family for SFTP, some traverse the public internet with TLS).[K
